insert_job: CVS_Batch_Window   job_type: CMD 
command: "cmd.exe" /c set
machine: CVS_FACE.B70PRODBAT0006
owner: batchprod.service@B70
permission: 
date_conditions: 1
run_calendar: CTS.Daily
start_times: "16:05"
condition: s(CVS_FACE_0360_450.ErUARunIRMAA)
description: "Scheduling Notes:  #Operator Notes: ##Title: ##Purpose:##Special Instructions##Escalations: Do not page if this job fails, just set to complete"
alarm_if_fail: 1
alarm_if_terminated: 1
group: CVS_FACE
application: FACETS-NOT-COUNTED.H
resources: (CVS_FACE.RC_BatchControl,QUANTITY=10,FREE=A)
